  "page": "Hunt of the Poor Fellows",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Hunt of the Poor Fellows</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/45_AC\" title=\"45 AC\">45&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">Kingswood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nVictory for the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a><br />Capture of <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poore\" title=\"Jeyne Poore\">Jeyne Poore</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b><br /></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Star_of_the_Faith.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/30px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/45px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/60px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a></b><br />\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Poor_Fellows.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Poor Fellows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/20px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/30px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Poor_Fellows.svg/40px-Poor_Fellows.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poore\" title=\"Jeyne Poore\">Jeyne Poore</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      scores of Poor Fellows</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>hunt of the Poor Fellows</b> was a campaign during the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hunt_of_the_Poor_Fellows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Late in <a href=\"/index.php/45_AC\" title=\"45 AC\">45&#160;AC</a>, the forces of King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> hunted down scores of <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a> that had taken refuge in the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">kingswood</a>. Many were sent to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> while those who refused to take the black were hanged.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The Poor Fellows were being led by <a href=\"/index.php/Poxy_Jeyne_Poore\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Poxy Jeyne Poore\">Poxy Jeyne Poore</a>, a woman considered a <a href=\"/index.php/Witch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Witch\">witch</a> by the three <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septons</a> of Maegor's retinue. She constantly eluded the king until she was eventually betrayed by three of her followers. The betrayers were pardoned and granted them <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighthoods</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Maegor the Cruel ordered that Jeyne be <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Jeyne_Poore\" title=\"Burning of Jeyne Poore\">burned alive</a> in a field by the <a href=\"/index.php/Wendwater\" title=\"Wendwater\">Wendwater</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hunt_of_the_Poor_Fellows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Template:Faith Militant uprising\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a